$Id$

The structure for the documentation is as follows:

- README: this document
- layout.txt: introduction and requirements definition
- api.txt: requirements specification
- design.txt: software specification
- integration.txt: a discussion on the integration of the library into a
  larger project

Software related documents:

- classdef.txt: introduces the class methodology used in implementation
  of the library
- sllist-tests.txt: software specification and test definition for a
  singly linked list

